{"tid":1396904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工黎做乜？","createTime":"2019-08-02T08:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T09:54:46.000Z","uid":277791,"like":4,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff0d3fbbf355c97a4c1ee0fbe1f6582c1671447","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"唔係主線為左證明香港人係可以拖到個經濟，用黎要求政府正面回應？<br />\n<br />\n睇到好多好似又要同公司傾又乜又物<br />\n<br />\n其實啲所謂上司公司，邊識處理。<br />\n大家請假 / 射波，唔係大家好做？<br />\n<br />\n當然，勁人就咁唔出現，或者工會搞既罷工，就梗係最 good 啦. 不過唔係人人有工會，做唔到最勁，都可以拎假支持呀！<br />\n<br />\n我理解錯？請指正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89b605181516935494a14b73b67bf6e2caf9039","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"真係負皮架喎<br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係負皮，話我知點解可唔可以？"},{"pid":"ebabaea283fdcb1bf7be0ff9de2eef0a11d368bf","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:06:17.000Z","msg":"其實我請左假，即係唔應該請假？"},{"pid":"ed40e371e1fa0011e14408138da0da5efe736d29","tid":1396904,"uid":246970,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"你冇得救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5999a4fc379e82cd0f1f0e605a3431b4762bf9f","tid":1396904,"uid":136640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"樓主中文拎1？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">已用不推文回覆</span>"},{"pid":"69ca4a7fa63751b8f5df8ac85cc62975f2f09b25","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed40e371e1fa0011e14408138da0da5efe736d29","tid":1396904,"uid":246970,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"你冇得救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"點呀？"},{"pid":"99631a9e62d6bc0b50e6a50b446c0e22a0649ab0","tid":1396904,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"從來對撚樣都係直接屌你老母"},{"pid":"3d9834e78379323bdb6ee0c5b364eef010641ea5","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5999a4fc379e82cd0f1f0e605a3431b4762bf9f","tid":1396904,"uid":136640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"樓主中文拎1？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">已用不推文回覆</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"wiki 話<br />\n<br />\n罷工行動，或被簡稱為罷工，是工人為了表示抗議，而集體拒絕工作的行為。<br />\n<br />\n放假咪拒絕工作？<br />\n<br />\n但我地罷工唔係針對自己公司，係針對個政權架嘛<br />\n諗唔通，射波有咩問題？"},{"pid":"d6cc619127b12f7a4b1648762f999e42c9a1268b","tid":1396904,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBgyC8o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBgyC8o.png&h=6650b859&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"832dbd414815312739426d76922f8acf487cca9a","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99631a9e62d6bc0b50e6a50b446c0e22a0649ab0","tid":1396904,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"從來對撚樣都係直接屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"唔係喎，明明啲公司都係收集員工請假計劃喎<br />\n<br />\n即係大家係認為，罷工就係乜都唔講，總之就星期一唔出現？"},{"pid":"e15e6cc00c705330e93c3c8272cd9b279fb34ddd","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6cc619127b12f7a4b1648762f999e42c9a1268b","tid":1396904,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBgyC8o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBgyC8o.png&h=6650b859&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"對唔住我係標題黨左<br />\n<br />\n己經請左星期一假，不過好似原來係唔應該請假？"},{"pid":"0e389c901e8695e7d1104d4fb8687307a27dbd02","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"呢次個3 罷<br />\n<br />\n罷工唔係總之就唔好返工<br />\n罷市唔係就係大家唔去買賣股票之類<br />\n罷課就唔返工，唔返學<br />\n（罷買就唔買野）<br />\n<br />\n拎假就唔叫罷？"},{"pid":"eda8c7a6ff5d320a904a19b098e70b574f576e62","tid":1396904,"uid":278647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"罷工即係香港市民唔返工唔做野<br />\n令香港既生產力下降 <br />\n令經濟放緩/倒退<br />\n從而強迫政府讓步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58eec941caf132dea73fd38baf9ae6215f65a25d","tid":1396904,"uid":277791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eda8c7a6ff5d320a904a19b098e70b574f576e62","tid":1396904,"uid":278647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"罷工即係香港市民唔返工唔做野<br />\n令香港既生產力下降 <br />\n令經濟放緩/倒退<br />\n從而強迫政府讓步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"係囉<br />\n咁射波 / 請假，都係唔返工唔做野<br />\n<br />\n但係樓上屌到仆街，負皮多過乜喎<br />\n唔太明點解"},{"pid":"5608f5484dab7be620f5d0a8b4cdadc2602db4c7","tid":1396904,"uid":278647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:38:30.000Z","msg":"可能你係近期先開始關心香港呢個家<br />\n但係呢度大部分人都覺醒左<br />\n知道200萬人和平上街勸政府撤回<br />\n都係一d用冇<br />\n所以先會搞到宜家咁<br />\n罷工，上街遊行/勇武，入立法會，不合作運動<br />\n以上目的都係想政府 改過自身<br />\n做番一個有公信力既政府"},{"pid":"3354953c9d997e39cde5f075d7fd958034821f4d","tid":1396904,"uid":294687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"樓主你up咩？"},{"pid":"043a55537e1c35ef374b1ced50933228ec87e6c8","tid":1396904,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re